WEBVTT

00:00:06.683 --> 00:00:08.643
my father.

00:00:44.262 --> 00:00:49.559
Can you hear that?
The screams within my heart.

00:00:50.643 --> 00:00:56.399
Can you hear that?
The voices of the forsaken.

00:01:10.205 --> 00:01:12.415
THE ROYAL PALACE -
ABOVE THE MAIN ENTRANCE

00:01:12.874 --> 00:01:13.875
What was that?

00:01:20.924 --> 00:01:22.884
THE ROYAL PALACE - MAIN ENTRANCE

00:01:28.181 --> 00:01:32.644
POST INVASION - THE SEIREITEI

00:01:32.686 --> 00:01:34.604
POST INVASION - URBAN AREA
What's causing all this shaking?!

00:01:34.604 --> 00:01:34.688
POST INVASION - URBAN AREA

00:01:34.688 --> 00:01:37.440
I'm not sure. I've never felt
anything like this before.
POST INVASION - URBAN AREA

00:01:37.440 --> 00:01:37.607
POST INVASION - URBAN AREA

00:01:38.233 --> 00:01:39.818
This can't be good...

00:01:40.360 --> 00:01:40.735
POST INVASION - OPEN AREA

00:01:40.735 --> 00:01:42.612
Did they remove the keystone...?
POST INVASION - OPEN AREA

00:01:42.612 --> 00:01:42.654
POST INVASION - OPEN AREA

00:01:42.654 --> 00:01:45.615
The keystone that holds
the three worlds together...
POST INVASION - OPEN AREA

00:01:45.615 --> 00:01:45.699
POST INVASION - OPEN AREA

00:01:46.324 --> 00:01:49.452
What are they up to...?

00:01:50.078 --> 00:01:50.495
MAYURI KUROTSUCHI'S PRIVATE LAB
REINFORCED WITH FLOODLIGHTS

00:01:50.495 --> 00:01:52.664
MAYURI KUROTSUCHI'S PRIVATE LAB
REINFORCED WITH FLOODLIGHTS
Is the place...shaking?

00:01:52.664 --> 00:01:52.747
MAYURI KUROTSUCHI'S PRIVATE LAB
REINFORCED WITH FLOODLIGHTS

00:01:52.747 --> 00:01:53.873
MAYURI KUROTSUCHI'S PRIVATE LAB
REINFORCED WITH FLOODLIGHTS
What the hell...

00:01:53.873 --> 00:01:54.207
MAYURI KUROTSUCHI'S PRIVATE LAB
REINFORCED WITH FLOODLIGHTS

00:01:54.207 --> 00:01:55.291
MAYURI KUROTSUCHI'S PRIVATE LAB
REINFORCED WITH FLOODLIGHTS
is going on?!

00:01:55.291 --> 00:01:55.417
MAYURI KUROTSUCHI'S PRIVATE LAB
REINFORCED WITH FLOODLIGHTS

00:01:55.458 --> 00:01:58.169
POST INVASION - STONE FORT SITE

00:01:58.211 --> 00:02:00.922
POST INVASION - NEAR THE RUBBLE

00:02:00.964 --> 00:02:03.633
ISHIDA RESIDENCE - RYUKEN'S ROOM

00:02:08.722 --> 00:02:10.682
KUROSAKI RESIDENCE

00:02:11.391 --> 00:02:12.684
This shaking...

00:02:13.601 --> 00:02:14.686
Can you hear that?

00:02:15.562 --> 00:02:18.523
It's the footsteps to a new world.

00:02:19.274 --> 00:02:24.154
I will put an end to
your endless humiliation.

00:02:28.742 --> 00:02:31.911
Yhwach...
We've come to stop you.

00:02:33.204 --> 00:02:34.664
I've been expecting you...

00:02:35.081 --> 00:02:36.750
Ichigo Kurosaki.

00:02:49.637 --> 00:02:54.726
<i>I put my hands together and pray</i>

00:02:54.809 --> 00:02:59.981
<i>Why is fate so cruel?</i>

00:03:00.065 --> 00:03:05.487
<i>My will to put on a brave face
is about to break</i>

00:03:05.570 --> 00:03:10.658
<i>Everything I do seems to go wrong,
you know?</i>

00:03:10.909 --> 00:03:13.495
<i>Oh, calm down,
I still have faith in you</i>

00:03:13.578 --> 00:03:16.373
<i>Even if we're apart</i>

00:03:16.414 --> 00:03:23.588
<i>Even if you forget about me someday</i>

00:03:24.589 --> 00:03:26.383
BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:03:26.925 --> 00:03:29.302
<i>We don't need words
to understand each other</i>

00:03:29.344 --> 00:03:32.263
<i>We're connected on a higher level</i>

00:03:32.305 --> 00:03:37.143
<i>I'm sorry, fate,
but you're full of it</i>

00:03:37.227 --> 00:03:39.813
<i>So let's laugh it off
by putting on a brave face</i>

00:03:39.854 --> 00:03:47.487
<i>With you, I think we can alter fate</i>

00:03:47.862 --> 00:03:53.118
<i>On lonely nights
when I feel like crying</i>

00:03:53.159 --> 00:03:56.955
<i>I will pray for you</i>

00:03:57.038 --> 00:03:59.916
<i>so that I won't leave you all alone</i>

00:04:16.194 --> 00:04:18.030
I foresaw this.

00:04:18.697 --> 00:04:22.951
You're here to stop me
from killing the Soul King, right?

00:04:23.452 --> 00:04:24.453
"Foresaw"?

00:04:24.953 --> 00:04:26.079
What's that supposed to mean?

00:04:26.621 --> 00:04:28.957
Kurosaki, is it me...

00:04:29.082 --> 00:04:30.083
or are his eyes...?

00:04:30.876 --> 00:04:32.169
What's up with those eyes?

00:04:33.253 --> 00:04:36.006
These are the eyes that see all.

00:04:36.548 --> 00:04:39.468
They are the proof
of a true Quincy.

00:04:39.801 --> 00:04:42.637
Everything rests in
the palm of my hand...

00:04:43.347 --> 00:04:47.225
The future of the Soul King
and your future as well.

00:04:48.852 --> 00:04:52.105
I won't let you.
That's what these powers are for.

00:04:52.564 --> 00:04:55.067
So you have two Zanpakuto...

00:04:55.734 --> 00:04:58.487
Go ahead, try and use them.

00:04:58.945 --> 00:05:01.823
Let's see if you can defeat me
with those blades...

00:05:01.990 --> 00:05:04.785
or if they will break once again.

00:05:23.136 --> 00:05:24.471
Getsugatensho.

00:05:55.252 --> 00:05:57.004
Nice try.

00:05:58.005 --> 00:05:59.297
Sankt Bogen.

00:06:18.025 --> 00:06:20.235
I see, Getsugatensho...

00:06:21.862 --> 00:06:24.740
That was pretty creative of you.

00:06:26.533 --> 00:06:27.701
However...

00:06:48.764 --> 00:06:50.849
What's wrong?
Aren't you going to fight back?

00:06:50.932 --> 00:06:55.812
If you fear, the only future
left for you is death!

00:06:55.854 --> 00:06:56.855
That right?

00:06:58.815 --> 00:07:00.567
Qualkreis.

00:07:07.741 --> 00:07:10.786
Rest in darkness once more, Ichigo.

00:07:16.750 --> 00:07:17.959
Getsuga...

00:07:18.210 --> 00:07:20.879
Sankt Zwinger!

00:07:21.505 --> 00:07:24.466
Jujisho!

00:07:39.356 --> 00:07:43.527
So that's Kurosaki's new power...?

00:07:57.165 --> 00:07:59.626
It's over, Yhwach.

00:08:02.087 --> 00:08:03.880
I see...

00:08:04.548 --> 00:08:09.720
Your training here has indeed
made your power grow stronger.

00:08:09.970 --> 00:08:14.224
You must have entered Irazusando
under Squad Zero's guidance

00:08:14.266 --> 00:08:20.439
to gain its everlasting memories
and revelations...

00:08:22.065 --> 00:08:23.275
How did you know...?

00:08:24.484 --> 00:08:26.820
But even that's not enough.

00:08:27.529 --> 00:08:29.823
Because I haven't used them yet.

00:08:30.198 --> 00:08:31.908
I have not...

00:08:32.784 --> 00:08:36.079
used my eyes
during our battle, Ichigo.

00:08:39.583 --> 00:08:41.835
The real battle starts now.

00:08:43.128 --> 00:08:44.671
It's time...

00:08:47.007 --> 00:08:50.135
for me to take action!

00:09:03.148 --> 00:09:04.816
Getsugatensho!

00:09:10.030 --> 00:09:11.365
I can see it.

00:09:17.913 --> 00:09:20.874
I can see your every action.

00:09:21.291 --> 00:09:23.710
But you cannot see it, do you?

00:09:24.544 --> 00:09:29.132
You cannot comprehend
the difference in our power.

00:09:31.093 --> 00:09:35.639
You finally see it, yet you still
turn your blade against me?

00:09:35.972 --> 00:09:37.474
How foolish.

00:09:47.234 --> 00:09:49.903
The more you turn
your blade against me,

00:09:49.986 --> 00:09:53.740
the more you will
fall into despair, Ichigo.

00:09:54.574 --> 00:09:55.742
I'll defeat you and protect-

00:09:55.826 --> 00:09:58.787
You will defeat me
and protect everything, is that it?

00:10:00.330 --> 00:10:02.916
How many times
must I repeat myself?

00:10:03.083 --> 00:10:06.253
I have seen everything
about your future.

00:10:30.569 --> 00:10:31.778
The tremors won't stop.

00:10:32.112 --> 00:10:33.405
What's going on?

00:10:33.697 --> 00:10:37.909
Urahara might know something.
Let's head to the Department of R&D.

00:10:38.118 --> 00:10:40.120
R-Right!
Was it this way?

00:10:40.245 --> 00:10:41.455
You fool.
It's this way!

00:10:42.956 --> 00:10:44.624
These tremors have been
going on for a long time...

00:10:45.042 --> 00:10:47.794
Think the other captains
and lieutenants are okay?

00:10:47.794 --> 00:10:51.798
Yes, of course.
You survived, didn't you?

00:10:51.923 --> 00:10:53.633
Hey, I guess you're right...!

00:10:53.759 --> 00:10:56.428
- Wait...
- Good job healing them.

00:10:56.636 --> 00:10:57.637
Thank you!

00:10:57.721 --> 00:10:59.931
Too bad you couldn't fix
her sharp tongue.

00:11:00.265 --> 00:11:01.266
No...

00:11:02.225 --> 00:11:03.935
S-Sorry!

00:11:04.102 --> 00:11:07.773
These unusual tremors,
and the change in the air...

00:11:08.106 --> 00:11:09.983
What is going on?

00:11:10.567 --> 00:11:12.819
It's no use
trying to figure it out.

00:11:12.986 --> 00:11:15.280
Now stop yapping
or we'll leave you behind.

00:11:16.448 --> 00:11:18.408
Hey! Who said you could
go on without us!

00:11:22.746 --> 00:11:23.747
Not yet...

00:11:24.539 --> 00:11:25.916
Don't die yet...

00:11:27.876 --> 00:11:29.628
Don't die yet...

00:11:37.094 --> 00:11:38.762
Urahara says we'll need

00:11:38.762 --> 00:11:41.932
tremendous amount of
Spiritual Pressure to create the gate.

00:11:42.015 --> 00:11:43.767
Can our equipment handle it?

00:11:43.767 --> 00:11:44.893
Mr. Urahara.

00:11:44.976 --> 00:11:46.228
Yes?

00:11:46.812 --> 00:11:49.898
The cause of this war
goes back to the conflict between

00:11:49.981 --> 00:11:52.776
the Soul Reapers and Quincies
from a thousand years ago, right?

00:11:52.984 --> 00:11:54.152
That's right.

00:11:54.194 --> 00:11:58.073
Then why did the Quincies
head to the Royal Palace

00:11:58.156 --> 00:12:00.033
without wiping out
the Soul Reapers?

00:12:06.790 --> 00:12:08.750
You must have seen it as well.

00:12:09.209 --> 00:12:11.962
The eternal world
that once existed...

00:12:12.421 --> 00:12:14.881
and the darkness
that threatened it.

00:12:15.298 --> 00:12:18.844
You saw the power of the Soul King
who could repel the darkness.

00:12:19.511 --> 00:12:23.640
However, even someone with
the power to overturn the world

00:12:23.724 --> 00:12:27.019
was being used to bring stability
to the world.

00:12:27.686 --> 00:12:30.147
He could see everything
in the three worlds

00:12:30.188 --> 00:12:33.775
even a thousand years into the future
with his discerning eyes.

00:12:33.859 --> 00:12:37.029
He even foresaw the tragedy
of us Quincies.

00:12:37.863 --> 00:12:40.907
Soul King Adnyeus saw it all.

00:12:41.283 --> 00:12:45.203
He saw it and still chose to
abandon the Quincies.

00:12:45.912 --> 00:12:49.416
The Quincies faced
near-extinction twice

00:12:49.499 --> 00:12:53.795
just because they did not fit into
the system of this world.

00:12:54.463 --> 00:13:00.344
So if the Quincy King stormed into
the Royal Palace,

00:13:00.427 --> 00:13:01.845
it could be for only one reason.

00:13:03.221 --> 00:13:06.183
This is why I have set my path.

00:13:06.808 --> 00:13:08.560
I will kill my father...

00:13:09.519 --> 00:13:14.066
and create a new world.

00:13:28.914 --> 00:13:33.543
Do you have a reason
to turn your sword against me?

00:13:34.711 --> 00:13:37.798
I came here to stop you.

00:13:38.590 --> 00:13:41.218
I came to stop you to protect
the Soul Society,

00:13:41.301 --> 00:13:42.886
the World of the Living,
Hueco Mundo...

00:13:43.345 --> 00:13:45.097
all of it!

00:13:46.640 --> 00:13:51.269
The Quincy blood in you
will never forgive the Soul King.

00:13:59.444 --> 00:14:00.654
Getsuga...

00:14:01.905 --> 00:14:04.825
I'm sorry, humans.

00:14:04.991 --> 00:14:07.994
...tensho!

00:14:09.371 --> 00:14:11.039
I'm afraid...

00:14:11.790 --> 00:14:14.960
you guys won't be able to
defeat Yhwach.

00:14:15.752 --> 00:14:17.671
But not to worry.

00:14:24.970 --> 00:14:28.640
That's what peace is all about.

00:14:29.766 --> 00:14:32.644
Isn't that right, Yhwach?

00:14:36.100 --> 00:14:38.927
THE THREE WORLDS

00:14:43.788 --> 00:14:48.460
You don't think Squad Zero
was wiped out, do you?

00:14:48.668 --> 00:14:49.753
I don't know.

00:14:49.961 --> 00:14:51.755
But there was enough
Spiritual Pressure back there

00:14:51.755 --> 00:14:53.214
to rock the entire Seireitei.

00:14:53.465 --> 00:14:55.884
What we can be sure of
is that someone in Squad Zero

00:14:55.967 --> 00:15:00.221
used their Bankai or something
just as powerful.

00:15:00.263 --> 00:15:03.933
So these ongoing tremors
are a result of that?

00:15:04.100 --> 00:15:05.935
That would be
the ideal explanation.

00:15:06.227 --> 00:15:07.896
But I'm getting a bad feeling...

00:15:08.813 --> 00:15:11.107
I just hope Ichigo and the others
are okay.

00:15:11.441 --> 00:15:13.818
What's with the long face?

00:15:13.985 --> 00:15:17.739
Those guys went up to
the Royal Palace

00:15:17.739 --> 00:15:19.449
to stop Yhwach at all costs.

00:15:20.075 --> 00:15:23.119
All we gotta do is believe in them.

00:15:23.870 --> 00:15:25.747
There's nothing to worry about.

00:15:27.916 --> 00:15:30.585
I didn't know you could
come up with such good advice.

00:15:30.669 --> 00:15:31.711
Right?

00:15:31.795 --> 00:15:33.963
Wait, what's that
supposed to mean?!

00:15:34.214 --> 00:15:37.759
Looks like everyone's also managed
to find their way to reach this lab.

00:15:40.387 --> 00:15:43.765
Welcome!
We've been expecting you.

00:15:44.349 --> 00:15:47.769
No you weren't.
Don't give us that, dumbass.

00:15:47.769 --> 00:15:50.271
I meant it.

00:15:50.522 --> 00:15:53.858
From here on, I really am
going to need all your help.

00:15:54.359 --> 00:15:57.779
Wait. Do you know
what's causing these tremors?

00:15:59.823 --> 00:16:01.533
I can't say for certain.

00:16:02.492 --> 00:16:04.744
But one thing I do know is that...

00:16:05.245 --> 00:16:08.957
these tremors are tied to
the safety of the Soul King.

00:16:09.708 --> 00:16:11.835
Protect everything, you say?

00:16:12.210 --> 00:16:13.920
Such arrogance.

00:16:13.920 --> 00:16:18.133
You think nobody but you
can do that?

00:16:18.466 --> 00:16:20.844
I don't care if someone else
can do it...

00:16:21.636 --> 00:16:25.015
that's not a good reason for me
to run from this fight!

00:16:25.682 --> 00:16:28.810
You intend to confront me
to protect the king

00:16:28.935 --> 00:16:33.565
knowing he is but a sacrifice
to stabilize the Soul Society?

00:16:34.024 --> 00:16:35.692
You sure like to talk.

00:16:36.985 --> 00:16:38.820
It leaves you full of openings.

00:16:39.529 --> 00:16:40.905
Touch them
and you'll be torn apart.

00:16:41.156 --> 00:16:42.157
So don't move.

00:16:42.824 --> 00:16:45.035
Tenshiheiso: Hissakikumoi.

00:16:53.168 --> 00:16:55.253
I foresaw it all.

00:16:56.421 --> 00:16:59.841
That you would meet
and resurrect Osho,

00:16:59.966 --> 00:17:04.179
or how you would show up here
at his urging...

00:17:04.929 --> 00:17:09.017
and that you arrived too late.

00:17:20.278 --> 00:17:25.116
<i>I will put an end
to your endless humiliation.</i>

00:17:25.867 --> 00:17:28.119
<i>Farewell, Soul King.</i>

00:17:28.995 --> 00:17:31.956
That's the Soul King?!

00:17:32.207 --> 00:17:35.835
You bastard!
Did you kill the Soul King?!

00:17:36.169 --> 00:17:37.253
No...

00:17:37.295 --> 00:17:38.546
He's still alive.

00:17:41.800 --> 00:17:43.134
- Kurosaki!
- Ichigo!

00:17:43.885 --> 00:17:47.931
Pull it out.
I know you can do it.

00:17:51.226 --> 00:17:53.728
Pull that sword out...

00:18:00.110 --> 00:18:05.323
and destroy the Soul Society
with your own hands.

00:18:10.203 --> 00:18:12.539
I foresaw this, Ichigo.

00:18:12.747 --> 00:18:18.962
The Quincy blood in you will never
forgive the Soul King's existence.

00:18:19.504 --> 00:18:23.258
It can't.
It won't.

00:18:23.758 --> 00:18:27.762
If the Quincy blood
courses through you...

00:18:28.430 --> 00:18:31.433
then you must slay the Soul King!

00:19:04.799 --> 00:19:06.968
Well done, my child.

00:19:08.470 --> 00:19:12.307
I gave you the Spiritual Pressure
that resided in my sword.

00:19:12.974 --> 00:19:16.519
It called to your blood.

00:19:17.145 --> 00:19:22.400
Your actions, your will,
your everything

00:19:22.484 --> 00:19:25.236
is connected with my will.

00:19:26.529 --> 00:19:30.158
To completely break
the Soul King's seal,

00:19:30.241 --> 00:19:32.952
I needed someone who possessed
the powers of Quincies, humans,

00:19:33.036 --> 00:19:37.082
Soul Reapers, Fullbringers,
and Hollows...

00:19:37.582 --> 00:19:43.088
I needed you,
who possess all of them.

00:19:43.755 --> 00:19:45.882
What...?

00:19:47.425 --> 00:19:51.012
Your awakening as a Soul Reaper...

00:19:51.304 --> 00:19:53.723
and attaining your true power...

00:19:54.224 --> 00:19:57.227
It was all for this exact moment

00:19:57.352 --> 00:20:02.357
for you to end the life of
the Soul King in front of my eyes.

00:20:04.025 --> 00:20:08.321
That...is the future I foresaw.

00:20:28.842 --> 00:20:29.884
These readings...!

00:20:47.027 --> 00:20:49.320
Still no news about
where the epicenter is.

00:20:49.779 --> 00:20:51.781
How can there be
an earthquake like that?!

00:20:52.115 --> 00:20:53.575
Maybe it's not a normal earthquake.

00:20:55.160 --> 00:20:56.703
Wait, are you saying...?!

00:21:02.542 --> 00:21:03.084
PASS

00:21:03.084 --> 00:21:04.085
PASS
Ichigo...

00:21:04.085 --> 00:21:05.503
PASS

00:21:11.134 --> 00:21:12.302
Could this mean...

00:21:13.219 --> 00:21:15.055
the Soul King is dead?

00:21:15.722 --> 00:21:16.806
We were too late?!

00:21:16.973 --> 00:21:19.768
No way...
What the hell is Squad Zero doing?!

00:21:20.894 --> 00:21:22.103
Mr. Ichigo...

00:21:22.395 --> 00:21:23.813
What happened to Mr. Ichigo?!

00:21:23.938 --> 00:21:25.690
Calm down, you fool!

00:21:26.191 --> 00:21:30.028
So what's going to happen now...?

00:21:32.030 --> 00:21:35.158
What is certain is that at this rate
the Seireitei, or rather...

00:21:36.201 --> 00:21:41.873
the Soul Society, Hueco Mundo,
and even the World of the Living...

00:21:43.541 --> 00:21:44.876
will all cease to exist.

00:21:52.467 --> 00:21:55.095
Come, Ichigo.

00:21:55.804 --> 00:21:57.138
Let us watch it together...

00:21:59.265 --> 00:22:03.645
the end of the Soul Society.

00:22:07.150 --> 00:22:10.737
<i>An ache upon
an unsatisfying grayscale</i>

00:22:10.821 --> 00:22:14.700
<i>My confidence vanishes</i>

00:22:21.373 --> 00:22:22.791
<i>I turned regret into lies</i>

00:22:22.791 --> 00:22:24.793
<i>I ignored our chipped blades</i>

00:22:24.876 --> 00:22:26.503
<i>I worked overtime
just for maintenance</i>

00:22:26.586 --> 00:22:28.463
<i>But I knew all along</i>

00:22:28.547 --> 00:22:31.883
<i>that this faded color
was an irreversible law</i>

00:22:31.967 --> 00:22:33.802
<i>So I might as well pray</i>

00:22:33.885 --> 00:22:35.637
<i>There's no turning back now</i>

00:22:35.679 --> 00:22:37.556
<i>I thought I had made up my mind</i>

00:22:37.681 --> 00:22:39.349
<i>but I'm still haunted by
doubt and anxiety</i>

00:22:39.474 --> 00:22:41.018
<i>A bundle of emotions torn to shreds</i>

00:22:41.143 --> 00:22:42.894
<i>with nothing left for me to gain</i>

00:22:43.020 --> 00:22:46.857
<i>What's more important
than one's life</i>

00:22:46.898 --> 00:22:49.735
<i>is to shoulder that burden
to sever this monochrome</i>

00:22:49.735 --> 00:22:54.740
<i>I keep searching for the answer
to an unsolvable thesis</i>

00:22:54.823 --> 00:22:56.867
<i>while making choices until I die</i>

00:22:56.950 --> 00:23:00.996
<i>Then I remember where we came from</i>

00:23:01.079 --> 00:23:03.915
<i>and the lives
that could never interact</i>

00:23:03.999 --> 00:23:07.627
<i>No one is allowed to use the scale
since it falls apart in an instant</i>

00:23:07.711 --> 00:23:11.048
<i>So, what can I measure
ourselves against?</i>

00:23:11.131 --> 00:23:15.344
<i>Instead, I hold onto your words</i>

00:23:15.427 --> 00:23:18.180
<i>that gave my heart meaning</i>

00:23:18.221 --> 00:23:19.473
<i>It's always a paradox</i>

00:23:19.556 --> 00:23:21.558
<i>The moon waxes
with each regret and sadness</i>

00:23:21.683 --> 00:23:25.270
<i>The massive, unconquerable foe is
the darkness that dwells within me</i>

00:23:25.395 --> 00:23:26.980
<i>I forsook my pride and joy</i>

00:23:27.105 --> 00:23:28.732
<i>but I am still confounded
by this flock of imperfection</i>

00:23:28.815 --> 00:23:30.609
<i>Beyond that white and resentful
midnight sun</i>

00:23:30.734 --> 00:23:32.736
<i>awaits an illusion etched in black</i>

00:23:35.658 --> 00:23:38.286
<i>"I was once you."</i>

00:23:38.744 --> 00:23:41.706
<i>"Soon, you will become me."</i>

00:23:42.748 --> 00:23:44.876
<i>"I can only pray the lives you carry"</i>

00:23:45.626 --> 00:23:47.795
<i>"are not a burden to you."</i>

